                    <h1 class="domdom">31</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/941">El Topo (1970)</a></h1>

                    <h2>31 Mar 2012, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Jodorowsky is El Topo, the black clad gunslinger and he's looking for trouble. The Midnight Movie sensation El Topo, like a cross between Sergio Leone and Siddharta, is not a classic for it's genre  - because it does not have one! </p>

