                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/955">Fando And Lis (1968)</a></h1>

                    <h2>5 Apr 2012, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>This tale of sadomasochistic love and unattainable paradise premiered at the 1968 Acapulco Film festival, inciting a riot that forced the director Alejandro Jodorowsky to flee for his life.</p>

